{{!-- preload all header backgrounds --}}
{{#each headers as |header|}}
  <img class="header-image {{if (eq header.id selectedHeader.id) 'visible'}}" src={{header.imageSrc}} alt={{header.title}}>
{{/each}}


{{!-- Title and subtitle --}}
<div class="container frontpage-header">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <img class="header-rtt-logo col-12 pt-0 pt-md-5" alt="RoboTeam Twente" src="images/rtt_logo_medium.png">
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="header-image-title text-white mt-5 pt-5">
        {{headerTitle}}
      </h1>

      {{#link-to 'crowdfunding'}}
        <span class="header-image-subtitle text-white mt-5 pt-5">
          We are currently running a crowdfunding campaign! Please support us by clicking here!
        </span>
      {{/link-to}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{!-- Articles --}}
<div class="container">
  <div class="row mt-5">
    {{#each articles as |article|}}
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-5 mb-md-5">
          {{#link-to article.link}}
            <img class="max-width" height="200" style="object-fit: cover" src={{article.imageSrc}} alt={{article.title}}>
            <h4 class="text-dark mt-2">
              {{article.title}}
            </h4>
            <span class="text-dark"> {{article.subtitle}} </span>
          {{/link-to}}
        </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
</div>


{{!-- Content --}}
<div class="container">
  <div class="row mt-2 mt-md-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-7 mt-3 mt-md-6">
      <h1> About us </h1>
      <p>
        RoboTeam Twente is a multidisciplinary team of students from the University of Twente.
        We aspire to innovate in both robotics and artificial intelligence.
        Next, we want to inspire everyone for these two sectors and show the world what can be achieved with them.
        We believe robotics and artificial intelligence can make the world a better place if used correctly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 mt-md-3">
      <h2 class="roboto font-weight-light font-italic mt-3 mt-md-5 pt-2 text-md-right mb-4 mb-md-0" > We use Robotics and Artificial intelligence to create the best robot soccer team in the world </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 mb-5">
    <p>
        Our medium to achieve these goals is the RoboCup, this year in Sydney.
        The RoboCup hosts multiple competitions for soccer and rescue robots as well as robots that can help at home or on the work floor.
        We will compete at the world championship of robot soccer in which two teams of eight small robots will compete with each other.

        This is the third year the team participates in the RoboCup. The team consists of students from different backgrounds,
        such as Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Biomedical Engineering, Computer Science, Advanced Technology and ATLAS University College.

        In the DesignLab of the University of Twente we have a special soccer field,
         on which we will frequently test our robots and in the near future play practice matches.
        If you don’t want to miss anything of our progress and if you want to be notified when we are going to practice, follow us on Facebook or Linkedin!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

